1. *Teret* je postao pretežak da bi se mogao prenositi. (The burden became too heavy to be carried.)

2. On je nosio *teret* kroz celu noć. (He carried the burden through the whole night.)

3. Ona je uzela *teret* na sebe da pomogne svojoj porodici. (She took the burden upon herself to help her family.)

4. Oni su bili opterećeni *teškim* teretom. (They were burdened with a heavy burden.)

5. On je izneo *teret* sa svojih leđa. (He relieved the burden from his back.)